    "metadata": {
        "type": "game",
        "name": "Predecessor",
        "steam_appid": 961200,
        "required_age": 0,
        "is_free": true,
        "short_description": "The tactical depth of a hardcore MOBA meets the explosive verticality of a third-person shooter. Master unique heroes, dominate the lanes in 5v5 combat, and join over 2,000,000 players in the ultimate free-to-play battleground!",
        "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>THE ULTIMATE MOBA EXPERIENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/b67f4e7aafa1c461ae1d9f5ca90eb12f.webp?t=1779195519\" width=1560 height=28 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TRUE THIRD-PERSON GAMEPLAY </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Predecessor isn't just a 3D MOBA - it redefines the genre completely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vault over enemies and terrain like never before - or leave the battlefield completely, taking to the skies to rain destruction on your opponents from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every wall, every structure, every angle is yours to exploit - if you can picture the play, you can break the game with it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/d7c717194de51f6c894e28b9cd956e4d.poster.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/d7c717194de51f6c894e28b9cd956e4d.webm?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/d7c717194de51f6c894e28b9cd956e4d.mp4?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE TRUE DEPTH &amp; SKILL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a diverse tapestry of over 45 complex playable characters who are expertly designed to be easy to learn but incredibly deep and rewarding to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from stance-shifters to summoners, gods to soldiers, knowing that your skills will always be rewarded, whether you're a seasoned competitive pro or an up-and-coming prodigy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/f2819fcc3498e14641d33b0e847a36d1.poster.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/f2819fcc3498e14641d33b0e847a36d1.webm?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/f2819fcc3498e14641d33b0e847a36d1.mp4?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JOIN A THRIVING COMPETITIVE COMMUNITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Squad up and throw down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a packed competitive scene blending community tournaments with official esports events, celebrating some of the best talent in the entire MOBA genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to compete at the highest level?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/54e1e5911ad363b7016a885c22bb2297.poster.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/54e1e5911ad363b7016a885c22bb2297.webm?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/54e1e5911ad363b7016a885c22bb2297.mp4?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENJOY A RICH, IMMERSIVE WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a cinematic rush every time you step onto the battlefield thanks to Predecessor's breath-taking visuals and sound design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy extraordinary graphical fidelity that pushes the limits of what a MOBA should look like, supported by awe-inspiring audio that lets you feel every explosion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/d0468eb4f1df4b64cfb66c058069b469.poster.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/d0468eb4f1df4b64cfb66c058069b469.webm?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/d0468eb4f1df4b64cfb66c058069b469.mp4?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WIN YOUR WAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike other MOBAs, Predecessor puts you in control - literally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a controller and hit the couch, playing effortlessly against friends and enemies on keyboard and mouse thanks to full cross-play on console and PC with Discord-powered voice comms, ensuring you never miss a callout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Squad up and play your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/72a3b1591bc9417bfb01656b279f87f9.poster.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/72a3b1591bc9417bfb01656b279f87f9.webm?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/72a3b1591bc9417bfb01656b279f87f9.mp4?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEVELOPED BY THE COMMUNITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Predecessor isn't just designed for the MOBA community, it's built <strong>by</strong> it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players drive Predecessor's development like no other game. Major decisions are polled, feedback dictates direction and transparency rules communication.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From our earliest days of being coded live on Twitch to being a global powerhouse in the MOBA genre, our community is at the heart of everything we do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/ffc0e40d26ad1fd57937cb19a37b521d.poster.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/ffc0e40d26ad1fd57937cb19a37b521d.webm?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/ffc0e40d26ad1fd57937cb19a37b521d.mp4?t=1779195519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/961200/extras/c0bca75b04c67da3a934dcbea39eb80c.avif?t=1779195519\" width=1560 height=163 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>JOIN OVER 2 MILLION PLAYERS NOW!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
